WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.410 --> 00:00:16.240
Namaste, I would like to invite you to
join me in a study of Patañjali's Yoga-

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:24.000
sūtra. This study will be in line with
 ancient traditions and wisdom

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:32.920
received from the great rishi's and
saintly yogis of the past. Each sūtra

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:41.170
will have word-for-word English synonyms
and a translation and commentary, in line

00:00:41.170 --> 00:00:47.860
with the earliest commentaries of known
commentators on the Yoga Sutra, beginning

00:00:47.860 --> 00:00:56.290
from Vyāsa, and also with the authentic
spiritual and philosophical traditions

00:00:56.290 --> 00:01:05.229
of my own lineage.This offering is meant
for those sincere seekers who are

00:01:05.229 --> 00:01:12.750
looking for deeper meaning and purpose
to their lives, and who aspire for true

00:01:12.750 --> 00:01:20.820
self-realization and God realization.
This will be an ongoing study with

00:01:20.820 --> 00:01:28.960
translations released regularly. So
please subscribe or follow, in order to

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:37.119
receive notifications of new video
releases. May we all benefit from this

00:01:37.119 --> 00:01:45.869
great and foundational sūtra on the path
of self-realization. Thank you.

00:01:52.390 --> 00:02:03.640
Oh Lord, lead me from illusion into the
eternal reality, from darkness into the

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:10.229
light, from death to the nectar of
immortality.

00:02:10.980 --> 00:02:17.730
Let there be the peace of spiritual
enlightenment.

00:02:22.660 --> 00:02:39.310
Auṃ asato-mā sad gamaya  Tamaso mā jyotir gamaya. mṛtyor māmṛtaṁ gamaya

00:02:39.310 --> 00:03:00.280
Aum śānti śānti śāntiḥ

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:04.710
 

